  <name>Puzzled</name>
  <summary>Do your best</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Inspired by Puzzle a Day, this application provides more variants and a
      solver to aid in your puzzling endeavours.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can drag the tiles with your mouse, rotate them with right-click, and
      flip them with middle, click. Move the tiles to fill the board in the
      middle to solve the puzzle for any day you like by leaving the desired
      cells free. You can select your target day at the top.
    </p>
    <p>
      When you select a day, the solver with predict, whether or not you can
      solve the day with the tiles currently placed on the board.
      You can disable this by clicking on the icon next to the target day
      selection.
    </p>
  </description>

